    <h3>Bug Description</h3>
  </div>

  <div class="yui3-editable_text-text"><p>It seems that cloud-init inherited from Fedora the inclusion of &quot;ssh_deletekeys: 0&quot; in cloud.cfg.tmpl (commit 41d46bfb85).  This is risky in orchestration environments where an instance might be used as a master or template, and cloned from without other tools removing SSH host keys.  We believe that line should be removed from cloud.cfg.tmpl to reduce the risk of it being used in such environments.</p>
